I've adopted this package, but I feel more like a foster parent.
Really I rescued it from the morgue, where its body was growing cold.
But I do not have the time to breath life into its body.  If anyone
who can love and cherish this sweet little morsel of code would like
to take it from the cabinet under the stairs to your warm home, please
be my guest.

